::Q1)write a code for small astrology based on your life path number for that get the date of birth from user then calculate life path number.(use switch case)
::calculation for life path number
::a=date%10
::b=date/10
::c=a+b

::if life path number
      ::1-lucky
	  ::2-carefully do your work
	  ::3-stronger
	  ::4-happy
	  ::5-can get help
	  ::6-doubt
	  ::7-sad
	  ::8-like
	  ::9-courage
	  
echo "Enter your Birth Date: "
read dayOfBirth
a=$(($dayOfBirth%10))
b=$(($dayOfBirth/10))
c=$(($a+$b))

if [ $c -ge 10 ]; then
  a=$(($c % 10))
  b=$(($c / 10))
  c=$(($a + $b))
fi

case $c in
1)echo "Lucky";;
2)echo "Carefully do your work";;
3)echo "Stronger";;
4)echo "Happy";;
5)echo "Can get help";;
6)echo "Doubt";;
7)echo "Sad";;
8)echo "like";;
9)echo "Courage";;
*)echo "invalid input";;
esac

